These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, monopoly
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the person playing bridge is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person playing whist is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Game    | whist    | monopoly | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, doctor, freelancer
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Job       | doctor | freelancer | lawyer |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, animation
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre         | animation     | mystery | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta  | 7up  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
House: tower, cape-cod, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the futuristic house is between the tower house and the canadian##2
2. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| House         | tower   | futuristic | cape-cod    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, go
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| Game   | go     | domino    | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing, reading
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Hobby           | fishing         | sudoku         | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, azalea
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person who growsmarigold##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Flower   | begonia | azalea | marigold |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

