The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the modern house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the cottage house##1
3. the person driving the trike is the modern house##1
4. the modern house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| House         | cape-cod | modern | cottage |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

