.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
House: art-deco, ranch-style, wooden
1. the wooden house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the australian is the wooden house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the wooden house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| House     | ranch-style     | art-deco   | wooden        |

