.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the french##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | french  | canadian | dutch   |
| Birthday         | october | november   | may |

