.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
City: new-york, colone, hannover
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to colone and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | colone | hannover | new-york |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
