.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, baking, reading
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Hobby      | hiking | baking | reading |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

