.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, turtle
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, car, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | hamster  | turtle   | guinea-pig |
| Transport   | ship | car | taxi       |

 